wing any existing marketing assets or videos you have<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"612\" data-end=\"683\">\n<p data-start=\"614\" data-end=\"683\">Clarifying your core message and what action you want viewers to take<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"684\" data-end=\"774\">\n<p data-start=\"686\" data-end=\"774\">Setting clear campaign objectives (e.g., drive signups, boost awareness, increase leads)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"776\" data-end=\"896\">If you\u2019re unsure of the best direction, we\u2019ll help define it, based on your current stage of growth and your competition.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"898\" data-end=\"935\">2. Audience and Platform Research<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"937\" data-end=\"1147\">We dive into audience data to ensure we\u2019re targeting the right users on the right devices, channels, and video content categories. Using Google Ads audience insights and third-party research tools, we identify:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1148\" data-end=\"1339\">\n<li data-start=\"1148\" data-end=\"1197\">\n<p data-start=\"1150\" data-end=\"1197\">Who your most profitable or engaged viewers are<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1198\" data-end=\"1238\">\n<p data-start=\"1200\" data-end=\"1238\">Where they\u2019re spending time on YouTube<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1239\" data-end=\"1287\">\n<p data-start=\"1241\" data-end=\"1287\">What videos and channels they frequently watch<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1288\" data-end=\"1339\">\n<p data-start=\"1290\" data-end=\"1339\">What content or messaging will resonate with them<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1341\" data-end=\"1521\"><strong data-start=\"1341\" data-end=\"1353\">Example:<\/strong><br data-start=\"1353\" data-end=\"1356\" \/>For an education client targeting high school leavers, we might target viewers of KCSE revision channels, using custom audience lists built from landing page visits.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1523\" data-end=\"1569\">3. Creative Development (or Collaboration)<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1571\" data-end=\"1584\">We\u2019ll either:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1585\" data-end=\"1825\">\n<li data-start=\"1585\" data-end=\"1697\">\n<p data-start=\"1587\" data-end=\"1697\">Create compelling video content from scratch (scripting, editing, motion graphics, subtitles, voiceover), or<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1698\" data-end=\"1825\">\n<p data-start=\"1700\" data-end=\"1825\">Work with your in-house team or existing video suppliers to adapt your current videos for YouTube advertising best practices.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1827\" data-end=\"1858\">Our creative team ensures that:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1859\" data-end=\"2117\">\n<li data-start=\"1859\" data-end=\"1918\">\n<p data-start=\"1861\" data-end=\"1918\">Key brand elements are shown within the first 5 seconds<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1919\" data-end=\"1981\">\n<p data-start=\"1921\" data-end=\"1981\">The video opens with a strong hook and maintains attention<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1982\" data-end=\"2044\">\n<p data-start=\"1984\" data-end=\"2044\">CTAs are clear, timely, and aligned with funnel objectives<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2045\" data-end=\"2117\">\n<p data-start=\"2047\" data-end=\"2117\">Multiple ad versions are created for testing and audience segmentation<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2119\" data-end=\"2212\">We design every asset with mobile-first, Kenyan user preferences, and attention span in mind.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2214\" data-end=\"2246\">4. Campaign Setup and Launch<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2248\" data-end=\"2346\">Once the creatives and targeting are finalised, we configure your campaign directly in Google Ads:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2347\" data-end=\"2674\">\n<li data-start=\"2347\" data-end=\"2427\">\n<p data-start=\"2349\" data-end=\"2427\">Set up campaign types and objectives (CPV, target CPM, maximise conversions)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2428\" data-end=\"2498\">\n<p data-start=\"2430\" data-end=\"2498\">Upload creative assets with properly structured naming conventions<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2499\" data-end=\"2558\">\n<p data-start=\"2501\" data-end=\"2558\">Add location filters, language settings, and scheduling<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2559\" data-end=\"2609\">\n<p data-start=\"2561\" data-end=\"2609\">Create custom audience segments and exclusions<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2610\" data-end=\"2674\">\n<p data-start=\"2612\" data-end=\"2674\">Integrate conversion tracking using Google Tag Manager and GA4<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2676\" data-end=\"2793\">Before launch, you\u2019ll receive a pre-launch checklist and approval review, so nothing goes live without your sign-off.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2795\" data-end=\"2837\">5. Monitoring and Weekly Optimisations<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2839\" data-end=\"2935\">We don\u2019t \u201cset and forget.\u201d Once your ads are live, we begin weekly monitoring and adjustments to:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2936\" data-end=\"3203\">\n<li data-start=\"2936\" data-end=\"2989\">\n<p data-start=\"2938\" data-end=\"2989\">Improve view rates and reduce cost per view (CPV)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2990\" data-end=\"3049\">\n<p data-start=\"2992\" data-end=\"3049\">Adjust targeting based on engagement or drop-off points<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3050\" data-end=\"3102\">\n<p data-start=\"3052\" data-end=\"3102\">Remove underperforming placements or ad versions<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3103\" data-end=\"3155\">\n<p data-start=\"3105\" data-end=\"3155\">Allocate more budget to high-performing segments<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3156\" data-end=\"3203\">\n<p data-start=\"3158\" data-end=\"3203\">Test new hooks or CTAs in creatives if needed<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"3205\" data-end=\"3295\">We share weekly summaries and flag any issues or wins early, so you\u2019re always in the loop.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"3297\" data-end=\"3342\">6. Monthly Reporting and Strategy Reviews<\/h3>\n<p data-st