ege admission content<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"922\" data-end=\"986\">\n<p data-start=\"924\" data-end=\"986\">Used remarketing to re-engage site visitors who didn\u2019t apply<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"987\" data-end=\"1043\">\n<p data-start=\"989\" data-end=\"1043\">CTA: \u201cApply Now\u201d leading to the admission landing page<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1045\" data-end=\"1059\"><strong data-start=\"1045\" data-end=\"1057\">Results:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1060\" data-end=\"1268\">\n<li data-start=\"1060\" data-end=\"1138\">\n<p data-start=\"1062\" data-end=\"1138\">430% increase in site visits from YouTube referrals during the campaign period<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1139\" data-end=\"1196\">\n<p data-start=\"1141\" data-end=\"1196\">64% view rate (well above industry benchmark of ~30%)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1197\" data-end=\"1268\">\n<p data-start=\"1199\" data-end=\"1268\">1,380 assisted conversions attributed via GA4 and YouTube integration<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"2069\" data-end=\"2123\">E-Commerce Brand: 3.5x ROAS on Flash Sale Campaign<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2125\" data-end=\"2284\"><strong data-start=\"2125\" data-end=\"2141\">Client Goal:<\/strong><br data-start=\"2141\" data-end=\"2144\" \/>A leading online electronics retailer in Kenya wanted to boost sales during a one-week flash sale, with a focus on smart TVs and headphones.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2286\" data-end=\"2305\"><strong data-start=\"2286\" data-end=\"2303\">Our Strategy:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2306\" data-end=\"2652\">\n<li data-start=\"2306\" data-end=\"2389\">\n<p data-start=\"2308\" data-end=\"2389\">Created skippable in-stream ads featuring product demos and limited-time offers<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2390\" data-end=\"2487\">\n<p data-start=\"2392\" data-end=\"2487\">Targeted custom audiences who had viewed or searched for similar products in the past 30 days<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2488\" data-end=\"2595\">\n<p data-start=\"2490\" data-end=\"2595\">Used conversion-optimised bidding (Maximise Conversions) with GA4 integration for real-time performance<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2596\" data-end=\"2652\">\n<p data-start=\"2598\" data-end=\"2652\">Layered in YouTube Shorts ads to increase mobile reach<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2654\" data-end=\"2668\"><strong data-start=\"2654\" data-end=\"2666\">Results:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2669\" data-end=\"2900\">\n<li data-start=\"2669\" data-end=\"2703\">\n<p data-start=\"2671\" data-end=\"2703\">3.5x return on ad spend (ROAS)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2704\" data-end=\"2770\">\n<p data-start=\"2706\" data-end=\"2770\">47% drop in cost-per-acquisition compared to previous campaign<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2771\" data-end=\"2830\">\n<p data-start=\"2773\" data-end=\"2830\">Inventory sold out 2 days ahead of the planned end date<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2831\" data-end=\"2900\">\n<p data-start=\"2833\" data-end=\"2900\">Over 5,000 new users added to remarketing list for future campaigns<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row full_width=&#8221;stretch_row&#8221; bg_type=&#8221;bg_color&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1717845133697{padding-top: 30px !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;}&#8221; bg_color_value=&#8221;#f4f4f4&#8243; el_id=&#8221;!\/contact&#8221;][vc_column]<div id=\"ultimate-heading-1950695ec1897fdba\" class=\"uvc-heading ult-adjust-bottom-margin ultimate-heading-1950695ec1897fdba uvc-2095  uvc-heading-default-font-sizes\" data-hspacer=\"line_with_icon\" data-hline_width=\"100\" data-hicon_type=\"selector\" data-hborder_style=\"solid\" data-hborder_height=\"5\" data-hborder_color=\"#3697ca\" data-icon_width=\"32\" data-hfixer=\"5\"  data-halign=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><div class=\"uvc-main-heading ult-responsive\"  data-ultimate-target='.uvc-heading.ultimate-heading-1950695ec1897fdba h2'  data-responsive-json-new='{\"